#. <section class="sutta" id="mn126"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "mn126:0.1"
msgid "Majjhima Nikāya 126"
msgstr "Middle Discourses 126"

#. </p><h1>
msgctxt "mn126:0.2"
msgid "Bhūmijasutta"
msgstr "With Bhūmija"

#. </h1></div><p>
#. <a class="nya" id="nya1"></a>
#. <a class="pts-vp-pi" id="pts-vp-pi3.138"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc1"></a>
msgctxt "mn126:1.1"
msgid "Evaṃ me sutaṃ—​"
msgstr "So I have heard."

msgctxt "mn126:1.2"
msgid "ekaṃ samayaṃ bhagavā rājagahe viharati veḷuvane kalandakanivāpe."
msgstr ""
"At one time the Buddha was staying near Rājagaha, in the Bamboo Grove, the "
"squirrels’ feeding ground."

#. <a class="nya" id="nya2"></a>
msgctxt "mn126:2.1"
msgid ""
"Atha kho āyasmā bhūmijo pubbaṇhasamayaṃ nivāsetvā pattacīvaramādāya yena "
"jayasenassa rājakumārassa nivesanaṃ tenupasaṅkami; upasaṅkamitvā paññatte "
"āsane nisīdi."
msgstr ""
"Then Venerable Bhūmija robed up in the morning and, taking his bowl and "
"robe, went to the home of Prince Jayasena, where he sat on the seat spread "
"out."

#. <a class="nya" id="nya3"></a>
msgctxt "mn126:3.1"
msgid ""
"Atha kho jayaseno rājakumāro yenāyasmā bhūmijo tenupasaṅkami; upasaṅkamitvā "
"āyasmatā bhūmijena saddhiṃ sammodi."
msgstr "Then Jayasena approached and exchanged greetings with him."

msgctxt "mn126:3.2"
msgid ""
"Sammodanīyaṃ kathaṃ sāraṇīyaṃ vītisāretvā ekamantaṃ nisīdi. Ekamantaṃ "
"nisinno kho jayaseno rājakumāro āyasmantaṃ bhūmijaṃ etadavoca:"
msgstr ""
"When the greetings and polite conversation were over, he sat down to one "
"side and said to Bhūmija:"

msgctxt "mn126:3.3"
msgid "“santi, bho bhūmija, eke samaṇabrāhmaṇā evaṃvādino evaṃdiṭṭhino:"
msgstr ""
"“Master Bhūmija, there are some ascetics and brahmins who have this doctrine "
"and view:"

msgctxt "mn126:3.4"
msgid "‘āsañcepi karitvā brahmacariyaṃ caranti, abhabbā phalassa adhigamāya;"
msgstr ""
"‘If you make a wish and lead the spiritual life, you can’t win the fruit."

msgctxt "mn126:3.5"
msgid "anāsañcepi karitvā brahmacariyaṃ caranti, abhabbā phalassa adhigamāya;"
msgstr ""
"If you don’t make a wish and lead the spiritual life, you can’t win the "
"fruit."

#. VAR: āsañca anāsañcepi → āsañca anāsañca cepi (aṭṭha.)
msgctxt "mn126:3.6"
msgid ""
"āsañca anāsañcepi karitvā brahmacariyaṃ caranti, abhabbā phalassa adhigamāya;"
msgstr ""
"If you both make a wish and don’t make a wish and lead the spiritual life, "
"you can’t win the fruit."

msgctxt "mn126:3.7"
msgid ""
"nevāsaṃ nānāsañcepi karitvā brahmacariyaṃ caranti, abhabbā phalassa "
"adhigamāyā’ti."
msgstr ""
"If you neither make a wish nor don’t make a wish and lead the spiritual "
"life, you can’t win the fruit.’"

#. VAR: kiṃvādī → kiṃvādī kiṃdiṭṭhi (s1) | kiṃvādī kiṃdiṭṭhī (s2, s3, km, mr)
msgctxt "mn126:3.8"
msgid "Idha bhoto bhūmijassa satthā kiṃvādī kimakkhāyī”ti?"
msgstr ""
"What does Master Bhūmija’s Teacher say about this? How does he explain it?”"

#. <a class="nya" id="nya4"></a>
msgctxt "mn126:4.1"
msgid ""
"“Na kho metaṃ, rājakumāra, bhagavato sammukhā sutaṃ, sammukhā paṭiggahitaṃ."
msgstr ""
"“Prince, I haven’t heard and learned this in the presence of the Buddha."

msgctxt "mn126:4.2"
msgid "Ṭhānañca kho etaṃ vijjati yaṃ bhagavā evaṃ byākareyya:"
msgstr "But it’s possible that he might explain it like this:"

msgctxt "mn126:4.3"
msgid ""
"‘āsañcepi karitvā ayoniso brahmacariyaṃ caranti, abhabbā phalassa adhigamāya;"
msgstr ""
"‘If you lead the spiritual life irrationally, you can’t win the fruit, "
"regardless of whether you make a wish,"

msgctxt "mn126:4.4"
msgid ""
"anāsañcepi karitvā ayoniso brahmacariyaṃ caranti, abhabbā phalassa "
"adhigamāya;"
msgstr "you don’t make a wish,"

msgctxt "mn126:4.5"
msgid ""
"āsañca anāsañcepi karitvā ayoniso brahmacariyaṃ caranti, abhabbā phalassa "
"adhigamāya;"
msgstr "you both do and do not make a wish,"

msgctxt "mn126:4.6"
msgid ""
"nevāsaṃ nānāsañcepi karitvā ayoniso brahmacariyaṃ caranti, abhabbā phalassa "
"adhigamāya."
msgstr "or you neither do nor don’t make a wish."

msgctxt "mn126:4.7"
msgid ""
"Āsañcepi karitvā yoniso brahmacariyaṃ caranti, bhabbā phalassa adhigamāya;"
msgstr ""
"But if you lead the spiritual life rationally, you can win the fruit, "
"regardless of whether you make a wish,"

msgctxt "mn126:4.8"
msgid ""
"anāsañcepi karitvā yoniso brahmacariyaṃ caranti, bhabbā phalassa adhigamāya;"
msgstr "you don’t make a wish,"

msgctxt "mn126:4.9"
msgid ""
"āsañca anāsañcepi karitvā yoniso brahmacariyaṃ caranti, bhabbā phalassa "
"adhigamāya;"
msgstr "you both do and do not make a wish,"

msgctxt "mn126:4.10"
msgid ""
"nevāsaṃ nānāsañcepi karitvā yoniso brahmacariyaṃ caranti, bhabbā phalassa "
"adhigamāyā’ti."
msgstr "or you neither do nor don’t make a wish.’"

msgctxt "mn126:4.11"
msgid ""
"Na kho me taṃ, rājakumāra, bhagavato sammukhā sutaṃ, sammukhā paṭiggahitaṃ."
msgstr "I haven’t heard and learned this in the presence of the Buddha."

msgctxt "mn126:4.12"
msgid "Ṭhānañca kho etaṃ vijjati yaṃ bhagavā evaṃ byākareyyā”ti."
msgstr "But it’s possible that he might explain it like that.”"

#. <a class="nya" id="nya5"></a>
#. VAR: muddhānaṃ → buddhānaṃ (mr)
#. VAR: satthā evaṃvādī → evaṃvādī evaṃdiṭṭhi (s1) | evaṃvādī evaṃdiṭṭhī (s2, s3, km, mr)
msgctxt "mn126:5.1"
msgid ""
"“Sace kho bhoto bhūmijassa satthā evaṃvādī evamakkhāyī, addhā bhoto "
"bhūmijassa satthā sabbesaṃyeva puthusamaṇabrāhmaṇānaṃ muddhānaṃ maññe āhacca "
"tiṭṭhatī”ti."
msgstr ""
"“If that’s what your teacher says, Master Bhūmija, he clearly stands head "
"and shoulders above all the various other ascetics and brahmins.”"

#. <a class="nya" id="nya6"></a>
msgctxt "mn126:6.1"
msgid ""
"Atha kho jayaseno rājakumāro āyasmantaṃ bhūmijaṃ sakeneva thālipākena "
"parivisi."
msgstr "Then Prince Jayasena served Venerable Bhūmija from his own dish."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="nya" id="nya7"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc2"></a>
msgctxt "mn126:7.1"
msgid ""
"Atha kho āyasmā bhūmijo pacchābhattaṃ piṇḍapātapaṭikkanto yena bhagavā "
"tenupasaṅkami; upasaṅkamitvā bhagavantaṃ abhivādetvā ekamantaṃ nisīdi. "
"Ekamantaṃ nisinno kho āyasmā bhūmijo bhagavantaṃ etadavoca:"
msgstr ""
"Then after the meal, on his return from alms-round, Bhūmija went to the "
"Buddha, bowed, sat down to one side, and told him all that had happened, "
"adding:"

msgctxt "mn126:7.2"
msgid ""
"“idhāhaṃ, bhante, pubbaṇhasamayaṃ nivāsetvā pattacīvaramādāya yena "
"jayasenassa rājakumārassa nivesanaṃ tenupasaṅkamiṃ; upasaṅkamitvā paññatte "
"āsane nisīdiṃ."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mn126:7.3"
msgid ""
"Atha kho, bhante, jayaseno rājakumāro yenāhaṃ tenupasaṅkami; upasaṅkamitvā "
"mayā saddhiṃ sammodi."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mn126:7.4"
msgid ""
"Sammodanīyaṃ kathaṃ sāraṇīyaṃ vītisāretvā ekamantaṃ nisīdi. Ekamantaṃ "
"nisinno kho, bhante, jayaseno rājakumāro maṃ etadavoca:"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mn126:7.5"
msgid "‘santi, bho bhūmija, eke samaṇabrāhmaṇā evaṃvādino evaṃdiṭṭhino—"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mn126:7.6"
msgid "āsañcepi karitvā brahmacariyaṃ caranti, abhabbā phalassa adhigamāya;"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mn126:7.7"
msgid "anāsañcepi karitvā … pe …"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mn126:7.8"
msgid ""
"āsañca anāsañcepi karitvā brahmacariyaṃ caranti, abhabbā phalassa adhigamāya;"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mn126:7.9"
msgid ""
"nevāsaṃ nānāsañcepi karitvā brahmacariyaṃ caranti, abhabbā phalassa "
"adhigamāyā’ti."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mn126:7.10"
msgid "‘Idha bhoto bhūmijassa satthā kiṃvādī kimakkhāyī’ti?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mn126:7.11"
msgid "Evaṃ vutte, ahaṃ, bhante, jayasenaṃ rājakumāraṃ etadavocaṃ:"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mn126:7.12"
msgid ""
"‘na kho me taṃ, rājakumāra, bhagavato sammukhā sutaṃ, sammukhā paṭiggahitaṃ."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mn126:7.13"
msgid "Ṭhānañca kho etaṃ vijjati yaṃ bhagavā evaṃ byākareyya—"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mn126:7.14"
msgid ""
"āsañcepi karitvā ayoniso brahmacariyaṃ caranti, abhabbā phalassa adhigamāya;"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mn126:7.15"
msgid ""
"anāsañcepi karitvā ayoniso brahmacariyaṃ caranti, abhabbā phalassa "
"adhigamāya;"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mn126:7.16"
msgid ""
"āsañca anāsañcepi karitvā ayoniso brahmacariyaṃ caranti, abhabbā phalassa "
"adhigamāya;"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mn126:7.17"
msgid ""
"nevāsaṃ nānāsañcepi karitvā ayoniso brahmacariyaṃ caranti, abhabbā phalassa "
"adhigamāya."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mn126:7.18"
msgid ""
"Āsañcepi karitvā yoniso brahmacariyaṃ caranti, bhabbā phalassa adhigamāya;"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mn126:7.19"
msgid "anāsañcepi karitvā … pe …"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mn126:7.20"
msgid "āsañca anāsañcepi karitvā … pe …"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mn126:7.21"
msgid ""
"nevāsaṃ nānāsañcepi karitvā yoniso brahmacariyaṃ caranti, bhabbā phalassa "
"adhigamāyāti."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mn126:7.22"
msgid ""
"Na kho me taṃ, rājakumāra, bhagavato sammukhā sutaṃ, sammukhā paṭiggahitaṃ."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mn126:7.23"
msgid "Ṭhānañca kho etaṃ vijjati yaṃ bhagavā evaṃ byākareyyā’ti."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mn126:7.24"
msgid ""
"‘Sace bhoto bhūmijassa satthā evaṃvādī evamakkhāyī, addhā bhoto bhūmijassa "
"satthā sabbesaṃyeva puthusamaṇabrāhmaṇānaṃ muddhānaṃ maññe āhacca "
"tiṭṭhatī’ti."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mn126:7.25"
msgid ""
"‘Kaccāhaṃ, bhante, evaṃ puṭṭho evaṃ byākaramāno vuttavādī ceva bhagavato "
"homi, na ca bhagavantaṃ abhūtena abbhācikkhāmi, dhammassa cānudhammaṃ "
"byākaromi, na ca koci sahadhammiko vādānuvādo gārayhaṃ ṭhānaṃ āgacchatī’”ti?"
msgstr ""
"“Answering this way, I trust that I repeated what the Buddha has said, and "
"didn’t misrepresent him with an untruth. I trust my explanation was in line "
"with the teaching, and that there are no legitimate grounds for rebuke or "
"criticism.”"

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="nya" id="nya8"></a>
#. <a class="pts-vp-pi" id="pts-vp-pi3.140"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc3"></a>
msgctxt "mn126:8.1"
msgid ""
"“Taggha tvaṃ, bhūmija, evaṃ puṭṭho evaṃ byākaramāno vuttavādī ceva me hosi, "
"na ca maṃ abhūtena abbhācikkhasi, dhammassa cānudhammaṃ byākarosi, na ca "
"koci sahadhammiko vādānuvādo gārayhaṃ ṭhānaṃ āgacchati."
msgstr ""
"“Indeed, Bhūmija, in answering this way you repeated what I’ve said, and "
"didn’t misrepresent me with an untruth. Your explanation was in line with "
"the teaching, and there are no legitimate grounds for rebuke or criticism."

#. <a class="nya" id="nya9"></a>
msgctxt "mn126:9.1"
msgid ""
"Ye hi keci, bhūmija, samaṇā vā brāhmaṇā vā micchādiṭṭhino micchāsaṅkappā "
"micchāvācā micchākammantā micchāājīvā micchāvāyāmā micchāsatī "
"micchāsamādhino te āsañcepi karitvā brahmacariyaṃ caranti, abhabbā phalassa "
"adhigamāya;"
msgstr ""
"There are some ascetics and brahmins who have wrong view, wrong thought, "
"wrong speech, wrong action, wrong livelihood, wrong effort, wrong "
"mindfulness, and wrong immersion. If they lead the spiritual life, they can’"
"t win the fruit, regardless of whether they make a wish,"

msgctxt "mn126:9.2"
msgid "anāsañcepi karitvā brahmacariyaṃ caranti, abhabbā phalassa adhigamāya;"
msgstr "they don’t make a wish,"

msgctxt "mn126:9.3"
msgid ""
"āsañca anāsañcepi karitvā brahmacariyaṃ caranti, abhabbā phalassa adhigamāya;"
msgstr "they both do and do not make a wish,"

msgctxt "mn126:9.4"
msgid ""
"nevāsaṃ nānāsañcepi karitvā brahmacariyaṃ caranti, abhabbā phalassa "
"adhigamāya."
msgstr "or they neither do nor don’t make a wish."

msgctxt "mn126:9.5"
msgid "Taṃ kissa hetu?"
msgstr "Why is that?"

msgctxt "mn126:9.6"
msgid "Ayoni hesā, bhūmija, phalassa adhigamāya."
msgstr "Because that’s an irrational way to win the fruit."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="nya" id="nya10"></a>
#. <a class="pts-vp-pi" id="pts-vp-pi3.141"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc4"></a>
msgctxt "mn126:10.1"
msgid ""
"Seyyathāpi, bhūmija, puriso telatthiko telagavesī telapariyesanaṃ caramāno "
"vālikaṃ doṇiyā ākiritvā udakena paripphosakaṃ paripphosakaṃ pīḷeyya."
msgstr ""
"Suppose there was a person in need of oil. While wandering in search of oil, "
"they tried heaping sand in a bucket, sprinkling it thoroughly with water, "
"and pressing it out."

msgctxt "mn126:10.2"
msgid ""
"Āsañcepi karitvā vālikaṃ doṇiyā ākiritvā udakena paripphosakaṃ paripphosakaṃ "
"pīḷeyya, abhabbo telassa adhigamāya;"
msgstr ""
"But by doing this, they couldn’t extract any oil, regardless of whether they "
"made a wish,"

msgctxt "mn126:10.3"
msgid ""
"anāsañcepi karitvā vālikaṃ doṇiyā ākiritvā udakena paripphosakaṃ "
"paripphosakaṃ pīḷeyya, abhabbo telassa adhigamāya;"
msgstr "didn’t make a wish,"

msgctxt "mn126:10.4"
msgid ""
"āsañca anāsañcepi karitvā vālikaṃ doṇiyā ākiritvā udakena paripphosakaṃ "
"paripphosakaṃ pīḷeyya, abhabbo telassa adhigamāya;"
msgstr "both did and did not make a wish,"

msgctxt "mn126:10.5"
msgid ""
"nevāsaṃ nānāsañcepi karitvā vālikaṃ doṇiyā ākiritvā udakena paripphosakaṃ "
"paripphosakaṃ pīḷeyya, abhabbo telassa adhigamāya."
msgstr "or neither did nor did not make a wish."

msgctxt "mn126:10.6"
msgid "Taṃ kissa hetu?"
msgstr "Why is that?"

msgctxt "mn126:10.7"
msgid "Ayoni hesā, bhūmija, telassa adhigamāya."
msgstr "Because that’s an irrational way to extract oil."

msgctxt "mn126:10.8"
msgid ""
"Evameva kho, bhūmija, ye hi keci samaṇā vā brāhmaṇā vā micchādiṭṭhino "
"micchāsaṅkappā micchāvācā micchākammantā micchāājīvā micchāvāyāmā micchāsatī "
"micchāsamādhino te āsañcepi karitvā brahmacariyaṃ caranti, abhabbā phalassa "
"adhigamāya;"
msgstr ""
"And so it is for any ascetics and brahmins who have wrong view, wrong "
"thought, wrong speech, wrong action, wrong livelihood, wrong effort, wrong "
"mindfulness, and wrong immersion. If they lead the spiritual life, they can’"
"t win the fruit, regardless of whether or not they make a wish."

msgctxt "mn126:10.9"
msgid "anāsañcepi karitvā brahmacariyaṃ caranti, abhabbā phalassa adhigamāya;"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mn126:10.10"
msgid ""
"āsañca anāsañcepi karitvā brahmacariyaṃ caranti, abhabbā phalassa adhigamāya;"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mn126:10.11"
msgid ""
"nevāsaṃ nānāsañcepi karitvā brahmacariyaṃ caranti, abhabbā phalassa "
"adhigamāya."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mn126:10.12"
msgid "Taṃ kissa hetu?"
msgstr "Why is that?"

msgctxt "mn126:10.13"
msgid "Ayoni hesā, bhūmija, phalassa adhigamāya."
msgstr "Because that’s an irrational way to win the fruit."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="nya" id="nya11"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc5"></a>
#. VAR: āviñcheyya → āviñjeyya (bj, s1-3, km, pts1)
msgctxt "mn126:11.1"
msgid ""
"Seyyathāpi, bhūmija, puriso khīratthiko khīragavesī khīrapariyesanaṃ "
"caramāno gāviṃ taruṇavacchaṃ visāṇato āviñcheyya."
msgstr ""
"Suppose there was a person in need of milk. While wandering in search of "
"milk, they tried pulling the horn of a newly-calved cow."

msgctxt "mn126:11.2"
msgid ""
"Āsañcepi karitvā gāviṃ taruṇavacchaṃ visāṇato āviñcheyya, abhabbo khīrassa "
"adhigamāya;"
msgstr ""
"But by doing this, they couldn’t get any milk, regardless of whether they "
"made a wish,"

msgctxt "mn126:11.3"
msgid "anāsañcepi karitvā … pe …"
msgstr "didn’t make a wish,"

msgctxt "mn126:11.4"
msgid "āsañca anāsañcepi karitvā … pe …"
msgstr "both did and did not make a wish,"

msgctxt "mn126:11.5"
msgid ""
"nevāsaṃ nānāsañcepi karitvā gāviṃ taruṇavacchaṃ visāṇato āviñcheyya, abhabbo "
"khīrassa adhigamāya."
msgstr "or neither did nor did not make a wish."

msgctxt "mn126:11.6"
msgid "Taṃ kissa hetu?"
msgstr "Why is that?"

msgctxt "mn126:11.7"
msgid "Ayoni hesā, bhūmija, khīrassa adhigamāya."
msgstr "Because that’s an irrational way to get milk."

msgctxt "mn126:11.8"
msgid ""
"Evameva kho, bhūmija, ye hi keci samaṇā vā brāhmaṇā vā micchādiṭṭhino … pe …"
msgstr "And so it is for any ascetics and brahmins who have wrong view …"

msgctxt "mn126:11.9"
msgid ""
"micchāsamādhino te āsañcepi karitvā brahmacariyaṃ caranti, abhabbā phalassa "
"adhigamāya;"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mn126:11.10"
msgid "anāsañcepi karitvā … pe …"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mn126:11.11"
msgid "āsañca anāsañcepi karitvā … pe …"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mn126:11.12"
msgid ""
"nevāsaṃ nānāsañcepi karitvā brahmacariyaṃ caranti, abhabbā phalassa "
"adhigamāya."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mn126:11.13"
msgid "Taṃ kissa hetu?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mn126:11.14"
msgid "Ayoni hesā, bhūmija, phalassa adhigamāya."
msgstr "Because that’s an irrational way to win the fruit."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="nya" id="nya12"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc6"></a>
#. VAR: matthena → manthena (bj) | mattena (mr)
msgctxt "mn126:12.1"
msgid ""
"Seyyathāpi, bhūmija, puriso navanītatthiko navanītagavesī "
"navanītapariyesanaṃ caramāno udakaṃ kalase āsiñcitvā matthena āviñcheyya."
msgstr ""
"Suppose there was a person in need of butter. While wandering in search of "
